attribute.name: formula
attribute.value: CMDCApprOPTx = if(CMDCApprOPB , "Approve OP COMPLETED.", "Approve OP NOT EXECUTED: The Approve OP checkbox was not selected.")

attribute.name: formula
attribute.value: CMDCSdSlsTx = if(CMDCSdSlsB , "Seed Sales COMPLETED.", "Seed Sales NOT EXECUTED: The Seed Sales checkbox was not selected.")

attribute.name: formula
attribute.value: CMLYRecRolATx = if(CMLYItmPentrp >= CMLYItmPentrThp , if(CMLYPrchFreqV >= CMLYPrchFreqThV, "dest", "occseas"), if(CMLYPrchFreqV >= CMLYPrchFreqThV, "rout", "conv"))

attribute.name: formula
attribute.value: CMFcRecRolATx = if(CMFcItmPentrp >= CMFcItmPentrThp , if(CMFcPrchFreqV >= CMFcPrchFreqThV, "dest", "occseas"), if(CMFcPrchFreqV >= CMFcPrchFreqThV, "rout", "conv"))

attribute.name: formula
attribute.value: CMLYRecRolBTx = if(CMLYGPV >= CMLYGPThrshp , if(CMLYSlsR >= CMLYSlsHghThrshR, "flag", if(CMLYSlsR >= CMLYSlsMedThrshR && CMLYSlsR < CMLYSlsHghThrshR, "cash", "main")), if(CMLYSlsR >= CMLYSlsHghThrshR, "core", if(CMLYSlsR > CMLYSlsMedThrshR && CMLYSlsR < CMLYSlsHghThrshR, "fire", "rehb" )))

attribute.name: formula
attribute.value: CMFcRecRolBTx = if((CMFcGPR/CMFcSlsR) >= CMFcGPThrshp, if(CMFcSlsR >= CMFcSlsHghThrshR, "flag", if( CMFcSlsR >= CMFcSlsMedThrshR && CMFcSlsR < CMFcSlsHghThrshR, "cash", "main")), if(CMFcSlsR >= CMFcSlsHghThrshR, "core", if(CMFcSlsR > CMFcSlsMedThrshR && CMFcSlsR < CMFcSlsHghThrshR, "fire", "rehb" )))

attribute.name: formula
attribute.value: CMHdSdSlsB = if(DRDVElapsedB || CMWPSdSlsB == FALSE, FALSE, TRUE)

attribute.value: CMHdApprOPB = if(DRDVElapsedB || CMWPApprOPB == FALSE, FALSE, TRUE)
